be.unamur.info.b314.compiler.main

Class SymTableFiller

  • java.lang.Object
    • be.unamur.info.b314.compiler.B314BaseListener
      • be.unamur.info.b314.compiler.main.SymTableFiller
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    be.unamur.info.b314.compiler.B314Listener, org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener

    public class SymTableFiller
extends be.unamur.info.b314.compiler.B314BaseListener
    This class mainly verifies the syntax of each context and fills the Symbol Table. Tests include Type verification, Indexation and whether a function exists or not.
    Author:
    Valentin Eggermont - valentin.eggermont@student.unamur.be, Thomas Vanhaeren - thomas.vanhaeren@student.unamur.be
